      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ORGANISED KAOS (4) hit the ground running off the inside draw with a fast early sectional but run over late and missed the frame when a 1.5 lengths fourth (29.14) over 498m at this track. Looks the one to beat on his best form. VALEENA BOY (2) showed strong early pace from the wide draw and stuck on well despite missing the frame, finishing fourth over 498m this track in 29.14. Shapes as one to consider. COMPLEX THINKING (5) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (21.71) at this track behind Exotic Ruby in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be in this for a long way. EMGRAND FLASH (1) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
